<br>
1) Level 29 Fire pet scroll - Purchasable in Mage guilds.  The level 29 pet was not research only.<br>
<br>
2) Words of Duress - Purchasable in Bazaar on Brell or can commonly be found on vendors in Firiona Vie.<br>
<br>
